{"tid":275293,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友追星追到傻撚左","createTime":"2017-06-08T02:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T15:13:48.000Z","uid":87536,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3d9e64b895d56ba0c8f1c5b5b604fdd9cb9f1a","tid":275293,"uid":87536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"平時無時無刻都係到睇啲韓星都算 <br />\n仲要成日拎我同佢地啲泡菜比 做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夠大隻 唔夠人地唱歌好聽 <br />\n大佬我咁犀利去撚左做明星啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後話要買禮物比佢地 接佢地機呢樣個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次接佢放學仲成程入左定落部電話到 我就係隔離on99咁 同佢講句嘢都好似阻住佢仆嘢咁 咁搞法遲早比條泡菜仔搞到分手到似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsorfor1999 不過真心泡菜害撚死幾多無知少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打記得係條女中毒之前以生命值阻止 唔係有排你受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db1a80b07ad93b267a62518fd5437a480cec109","tid":275293,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:26:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾識垃圾"},{"pid":"793fe250496e307daaf01585a60178b2eeb975ba","tid":275293,"uid":87536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾識垃圾</blockquote><br />\n未去到咁偏激 不過泡菜真害人居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地明星係正面先值得追 依家啲人連偶像吸毒做錯事都護主護到好似冇錯咁 就真係錯撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：只針對個別例子 請對號入座"},{"pid":"e98d66fd5e1eea23064cf4efe38741c4f1ee8927","tid":275293,"uid":100626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚多要求 你送塊鏡被佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312dec61581d8f483179a455207fda1677235254","tid":275293,"uid":68148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"<bl